                    "name": "Sudden Slices",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The faceless butcher is <a aonid=\"39\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">undetected</a> by their target; <b>Effect</b> The faceless butcher Strides once and makes two cleaver Strikes against the target. During the Stride, they gain a +10-foot circumstance bonus to their Speed.",
